          <p class="min-w-full">The kind of furniture that gets better with every passing year.</p>
          <p class="w-[486px]">Each one starts as reclaimed teak with its own story. We shape it, build around it, and finish it by hand. Designed to feel like it's always belonged, and built to prove it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Highlight trio + filler -->
    <div class="bg-[#fdfcfb] flex flex-col items-start py-[160px] w-full">
